---
description: Documentation and portfolio guidance for markdown files
globs: ["README.md", "docs/**/*.md"]
---

Treat documentation in this repository as portfolio material.

Documentation should:
- start with the practical goal
- say what skill is being demonstrated
- explain major design choices briefly
- mention tradeoffs where relevant
- stay concise and readable

Avoid:
- generic filler
- long theory dumps with no practical connection
- unexplained complexity
